description:
PODCAST SUMMARY HOUR 2:

Buck to join Clay at Ole Miss-Alabama game. Manchin and Sinema stymie Dems on spending. Designer of AOC's Tax the Rich dress owes back taxes. Data proves seasonal flu is way more dangerous to kids than covid. Covid deaths among children are infinitesimal, and yet we're masking, restricting and vaccinating kids. C&B take calls.
